<P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><ENDNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><AUTONUM Number="1" NumberType="Endnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>[해설] 주어진 조건 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000058" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1058"><SIZE Height="1350" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4600" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>x+y = sqrt {3}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000059" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1059"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3800" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>xy = -3</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>을 이용하여 식의 값을 구하는 과정은 다음과 같습니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>1. 구하고자 하는 식을 통분하여 정리합니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="65" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000060" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1060"><SIZE Height="3000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="9350" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>x^{2}} over {y} - {y^{2}} over {x} = {x^{3} - y^{3}} over {xy</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>2. </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000061" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1061"><SIZE Height="1350" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3400" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>x^{3} - y^{3}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>의 값을 구하기 위해 먼저 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000062" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1062"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2200" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>x - y</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>의 값을 구합니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000063" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1063"><SIZE Height="1350" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="11200" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>(x - y)^{2} = (x + y)^{2} - 4xy</SCRIPT></EQUATION><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000064" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1064"><SIZE Height="1350" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="17700" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>(x - y)^{2} = ( sqrt {3})^{2} - 4(-3) = 3 + 12 = 15</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>이때 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000065" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1065"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2200" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" Ve