<P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><ENDNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><AUTONUM Number="1" NumberType="Endnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>[해설] 1. 조건 (가)에서 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000113" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1113"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7300" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(-x) + f(x) = 0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>이므로 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000114" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1114"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6700" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(-x) = -f(x)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>입니다. 즉, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000115" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1115"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1850" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(x)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 기함수(홀함수)이며 홀수 차수의 항으로만 구성됩니다. 최고차항의 계수가 1인 삼차다항식이므로 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000116" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1116"><SIZE Height="1350" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6250" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(x) = x^{3} + ax</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>(단, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000117" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1117"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="600" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>a</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 상수)로 놓을 수 있습니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>2. 조건 (나)에서 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000118" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1118"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6200" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>g(-x) = g(x)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>이므로 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000119" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1119"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2100" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>g(x)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 우함수(짝함수)이며 짝수 차수의 항과 상수항으로만 구성됩니다. 최고차항의 계수가 2인 이차다항식이므로 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000120" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1120"><SIZE Height="1350" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6500" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>g(x) = 2x^{2} + b</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>(단, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000121" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1121"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="600" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>b</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 상수)로 놓을 수 있습니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>3. 조건 (다)에서 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000122" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1122"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4950" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(x) + g(x)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>가 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000123" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1123"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2200" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>x - 1</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>로 나누어떨어지므로 나머지 정리에 의해 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000124" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1124"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6550" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(1) + g(1) = 0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>입니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000125" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1125"><SIZE Height="1350" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="10350" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(1) = 1^{3} + a(1) = 1 + a</SCRIPT></EQUATION><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000126" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1126"><SIZE Height="1350" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="10600" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>g(1) = 2(1)^{2} + b = 2 + b</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>따라서 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000127" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1127"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="8800" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>(1 + a) + (2 + b) = 0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>에서 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000128" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1128"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4800" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>a + b = -3</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>임을 알 수 있습니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>4. 구하고자 하는 값 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000129" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1129"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="5550" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(2) + 2g(2)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>를 계산해 봅시다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000130" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1130"><SIZE Height="1350" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="10950" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(2) = 2^{3} + a(2) = 8 + 2a</SCRIPT></EQUATION><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000131" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1131"><SIZE Height="1350" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="10600" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>g(2) = 2(2)^{2} + b = 8 + b</SCRIPT></EQUATION><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000132" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1132"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="30050" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(2) + 2g(2) = (8 + 2a) + 2(8 + b) = 8 + 2a + 16 + 2b = 24 + 2(a + b)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>5. 위에서 구한 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000133" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1133"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4800" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>a + b = -3</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>을 대입하면,</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000134" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1134"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="11300" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>24 + 2(-3) = 24 - 6 = 18</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>따라서 정답은 ④입니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></ENDNOTE><CHAR> 최고차항의 계수가 1인 삼차다항식 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000135" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1135"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1850" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(x)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>와 최고차항의 계수가 2인 이차다항식 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000136" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1136"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2100" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>g(x)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>가 다음 조건을 만족시킨다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>(가) 모든 실수 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000137" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1137"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="600" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>x</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>에 대하여 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000138" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1138"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRe