n" ZOrder="1184"><SIZE Height="2600" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="16702" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(x) = {1} over {2}(x-3)(2Q(x)+4) - 2(x-3) + R</SCRIPT></EQUATION><EQUATION BaseLine="65" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000185" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1185"><SIZE Height="2600" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="15937" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(x) = {1} over {2}(x-3)(2Q(x)+4) - 2x + 6 + R</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>3. 이때 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000186" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1186"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1850" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(x)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 사차다항식이므로 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000187" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1187"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2300" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>Q(x)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 삼차다항식입니다. 따라서 나누는 식 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000188" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1188"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4500" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>2Q(x)+4</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>도 삼차다항식입니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>4. 나머지에 해당하는 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000189" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1189"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="5400" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>-2x + 6 + R</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>은 일차식이므로 나누는 식(삼차식)보다 차수가 낮아 적절한 나머지입니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>5. 따라서 </CHAR><EQUATI