R></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>주어진 범위 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000278" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1278"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="5300" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>-n le x le 2n</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>에서 축 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="65" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000279" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1279"><SIZE Height="2600" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6205" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>x = {3n} over {2} = 1.5n</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>이 포함됩니다. 이차함수의 최고차항의 계수가 음수이므로 위로 볼록한 포물선이며, 최댓값은 꼭짓점에서 가집니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="65" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000280" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1280"><SIZE Height="3000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="24862" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>M = f(1.5n) = -(1.5n)^{2} + 3n(1.5n) + b = 2.25n^{2} + b = {9} over {4}n^{2} + b</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>최솟값은 축에서 가장 멀리 떨어진 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000281" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1281"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3200" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>x = -n</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>에서 가집니다. (축 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000282" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1282"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2100" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>1.5n</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>에서 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000283" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1283"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1600" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>-n</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>까지의 거리는 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000284" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1284"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2100" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>2.5n</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000285" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1285"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1200" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>2n</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>까지의 거리는 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000286" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1286"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2100" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>0.5n</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>이므로 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000287" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1287"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3200" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>x = -n</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>이 더 멉니다.)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000288" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1288"><SIZE Height="1350" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="29050" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>m = f(-n) = -(-n)^{2} + 3n(-n) + b = -n^{2} - 3n^{2} + b = -4n^{2} + b</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>따라서 최댓값과 최솟값의 차는 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="65" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000289" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1289"><SIZE Height="3000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="16660" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>M - m = ({9} over {4}n^{2} + b) - (-4n^{2} + b) = {25} over {4}n^{2}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>입니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>즉, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="65" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000290" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1290"><SIZE Height="3000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="5865" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>k(n) = {25} over {4}n^{2}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>입니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>4. 최종 값 계산</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="65" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000291" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1291"><SIZE Height="2600" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7055" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>g(2) = {3 TIMES 2} over {2} = 3</SCRIPT></EQUATION><EQUATION BaseLine="65" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000292" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1292"><SIZE Height="3000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="9265" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>h(2) = -{9 TIMES 2^{2}} over {4} = -9</SCRIPT></EQUATION><EQUATION BaseLine="65" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000293" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1293"><SIZE Height="3000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="8585" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>k(2) = {25 TIMES 2^{2}} over {4} = 25</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>따라서 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000294" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1294"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="15900" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>g(2) + h(2) + k(2) = 3 - 9 + 25 = 19</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>입니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></ENDNOTE><CHAR> 다음은 모든 실수 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000295" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1295"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="600" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>x</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>에 대하여 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000296" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1296"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6900" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(x) = f(3n - x)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>를 만족시키는 이차함수 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000297" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1297"><SIZE Height="1350" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="8850" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(x) = -x^{2} + ax + b</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>에 대한 설명이다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT