<P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><ENDNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><AUTONUM Number="1" NumberType="Endnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>[해설] 이차방정식 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000535" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1535"><SIZE Height="1350" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6600" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>x^{2} - 3x + 5 = 0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>의 두 근이 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000536" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1536"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1500" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>alpha , beta</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>이므로 다음이 성립합니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000537" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1537"><SIZE Height="1350" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="11900" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>alpha ^{2} - 3 alpha + 5 = 0 , alpha ^{2} + 5 = 3 alpha</SCRIPT></EQUATION><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000538" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1538"><SIZE Height="1350" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="11900" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>beta ^{2} - 3 beta + 5 = 0 , beta ^{2} + 5 = 3 beta</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>주어진 식의 분모를 변형하면 다음과 같습니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000539" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1539"><SIZE Height="1350" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="17900" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>alpha ^{2} - 2 alpha + 5 = ( alpha ^{2} + 5) - 2 alpha = 3 alpha - 2 alpha = alpha</SCRIPT></EQUATION><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000540" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1540"><SIZE Height="1350" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="17900" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>beta ^{2} - 2 beta + 5 = ( beta ^{2} + 5) - 2 beta = 3 beta - 2 beta = beta</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>따라서 구하고자 하는 식은 다음과 같이 정리됩니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="65" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000541" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1541"><SIZE Height="3000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="18530" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>1} over { alpha ^{2} - 2 alpha + 5} + {1} over { beta ^{2} - 2 beta + 5} = {1} over { alpha } + {1} over { beta } = { alpha + beta } over { alpha beta</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>이차방정식의 근과 계수의 관계에 의해</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000542" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1542"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3800" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>alpha + beta = 3</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000543" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1543"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2800" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>alpha beta = 5</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>이 값들을 대입하면</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="65" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000544" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1544"><SIZE Height="2600" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="5440" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>alpha + beta } over { alpha beta } = {3} over {5</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>따라서 정답은 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="65" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000545" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1545"><SIZE Height="2600" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1700" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>3} over {5</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>입니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></ENDNOTE><CHAR> 이차방정식 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000546" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1546"><SIZE Height="1350" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6600" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>x^{2} - 3x + 5 = 0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>의 서로 다른 두 근을 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000547" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1547"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1500" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>alpha , beta</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>라 할 때, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="65" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000548" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1548"><SIZE Height="3000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="11050" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>1} over { alpha ^{2} - 2 alpha + 5} + {1} over { beta ^{2} - 2 beta + 5</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>의 값을 구하시오. [서]</CHAR></TEXT></P>
<P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><ENDNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><AUTONUM Number="1" NumberType="Endnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>[해설] 주어진 등식 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000549" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1549"><SIZE Height="1350" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="9000" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>a^{3} + b^{3} + c^{3} = 3abc</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>에서 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1000000550" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1550"><SIZE Height="1350" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="10600" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT/></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>a^{3} + b^{3} + c^{3} - 3abc = 0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>입니다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>인수분해 공식을 이용하면</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1